{
  "id": null,
  "uid": "mycelium-stages",
  "title": "mycelium — stages",
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "version": 1,
  "editable": true,
  "refresh": "10s",
  "time": { "from": "now-30m", "to": "now" },
  "tags": ["lab", "guest", "mycelium"],
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Stage throughput (processed/s by stage)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "ops" }, "overrides": [] },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum by (stage) (rate(chunks_processed[2m]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{stage}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Stage duration p95 (by stage)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 0 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "s" }, "overrides": [] },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum by (le, stage) (rate(stage_duration_seconds_bucket[5m])))",
          "legendFormat": "{{stage}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Stage queue depth (km.stage.* on vhost mycelium)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 8 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "short" }, "overrides": [] },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "rabbitmq_queue_messages{vhost=\"mycelium\", queue=~\"km\\\\.stage\\\\.[^.]+\"}",
          "legendFormat": "{{queue}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Dead-letter depth (km.stage.*.dlq on vhost mycelium)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 8 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "short" }, "overrides": [] },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "rabbitmq_queue_messages{vhost=\"mycelium\", queue=~\"km\\\\.stage\\\\..+\\\\.dlq\"}",
          "legendFormat": "{{queue}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "About this dashboard",
      "gridPos": { "h": 6, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 16 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "Stage counters/durations come from mycelium's Prometheus `/metrics` (the stages surface of its consolidated FastAPI). Metric names are pinned to mycelium's real, **unprefixed** collectors (recon 2026-07-20): `chunks_processed` (label `stage`) and the `stage_duration_seconds` histogram — verify the histogram type when the KM-2 image lands. Queue panels read the LAB's shared RabbitMQ exporter for the `mycelium` vhost (the KM-4 queue-mode target topology, owned by the lab's generator, ADR-007.4); depths stay 0 until queue-mode publishes. In fake mode (EXP-70, once KM-1 lands) stages drain with zero LLM spend."
      }
    }
  ]
}
